TriggerLogic.Name: Custom Action (Alternate)
TriggerLogic.CodeStr: local x = 3000 - 100 local y = 500 local z = -50 for i=1,3 do x = x + 144 z = z + 50 local unitID = Spring.CreateUnit("corhurc2", x, y, z, "s", 0) Spring.SetUnitPosition(unitID, x, y, z - 500) Spring.GiveOrderToUnit(unitID, CMD.MOVE, {x, y, z +5000}, {}) end
